discovered during a search of the farm buildings.
   Authorities have warned of more possible attacks and stepped up
searches for terrorists since Herrhausen was killed Nov. 30.
   The Red Army Faction, which has carried out attacks against
government, military and business targets in West Germany for more
than 15 years, has claimed responsibility for killing Herrhausen.
