<HEAD>Groups Block State Siting Commission Inspections</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: SUBS lead to CORRECT dateline community to ANGELICA, sted ALLEN;
the site of the protest is in ANGELICA, a hamlet within the town of Allen.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By HILARY APPELMAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>ANGELICA, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   State officials vowed they would fare
better on their next visit to a potential radioactive waste dump
site after they were chased and cornered for five hours Wednesday
by anti-dump protesters.
