<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
</TEXT>
<NOTE>1990 Lexus LS 400</NOTE>
<TEXT>
   
   BASE PRICE: $35,000.
   AS TESTED: $41,325.
   
   TYPE: Front-engine, rear-drive, 5-passenger luxury sedan.
   ENGINE: 4-liter, 32-valve, port fuel-injected V8.
